d2_dictionary.application_names: OpenText Life Sciences Medical Device Solution¬OpenText Life Sciences Medical Device for Quality and Manufacturing Solution¬OpenText Life Sciences Submission Storage and Viewing¬OpenText Life Sciences Research and Development Solution¬OpenText Life Sciences Quality and Manufacturing Solution
d2_dictionary.dql: select distinct v.object_name as name, v.locale_value as label_en from d2_dictionary_value v, d2_dictionary d where d.object_name = v.dictionary_name and d.object_name = 'Geographic Regions' and any v.locale_value is not nullstring and v.object_name = (SELECT distinct region FROM cd_reg_admin_info WHERE application_description='$value(application_descriptions)') and v.i_position = d.i_position order by locale_value enable (ROW_BASED)
